        "created_at": "2019-06-19T08:44:59.094Z",
        "cooked": "<p>There are no out of the box solutions for this. It should be possible with some clever SQL queries on the live database, or some manipulation of the backup files, but AFAIK no one has ever implemented that.</p>",
