        "cooked": "<p>I‚Äôm bumping into this too with people coming back and hiding their account‚Äôs phone number (now that usernames are a thing).</p>\n<p>I have old chat histories that don‚Äôt get merged because Signal can‚Äôt realize they‚Äôre the same user automatically.</p>",
