        "created_at": "2025-03-29T20:13:27.139Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Just had one of my contacts make a new account literally today, so kind of a coincidence I‚Äôm seeing this thread now. I think it could get messy, but it would be nice to be able to merge chats from multiple accounts into one. Maybe the merge can be done only on the frontend so the data will still be separate in the database and can be ‚Äúunmerged‚Äù in the future if needed.</p>",
